Billionaire, Elon Musk, has expressed his excitement at meeting the head of the Catholic Church, Pope Francis.
Sharing a photo on his Twitter handle on Saturday, Musk, who was on the visit with his teenage children said, “Honored to meet #Pontifex yesterday.”
Musk’s visit comes a week after his son Xavier legally changed gender from male to female and dropped last name to distance herself from father.
